13
00:00:58,739 --> 00:01:03,270
So, is fear an effective way to change people’s attitudes?

14
00:01:03,270 --> 00:01:10,640
Janis and Feshbach in 1953 varied the extent of fear in a message about proper tooth care.

15
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:16,220
They gave their participants a 15 minute lecture about dental hygiene accompanied by illustrated

16
