29
00:02:12,690 --> 00:02:17,780
dental hygiene, but instead participants were given information about how teeth develop

30
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:19,810
and what functions they served.

31
00:02:19,810 --> 00:02:24,500
The researchers then measured how much participants conformed to the message, how much they were

